OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMiner Glencore pays $180m  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin latest corruption case  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Swiss-based mining company,        
OL,6, Glencore, has said it will pay $180m   
OL,7, (#147m) to the Democratic Republic of  
OL,8, Congo to settle corruption claims.     
OL,10,FThe agreement covers an 11-year period 
OL,11,Ffrom 2007 to 2018.                     
OL,13,FIt is the latest in a series of        
OL,14,Fcorruption cases which has seen        
OL,15,FGlencore agree to pay out more than    
OL,16,F$1.6bn in fines this year.             
OL,18,FIn May it admitted bribing officials in
OL,19,Fseveral African nations including DR   
OL,20,FCongo (DRC).                           
